creator: TRAINERIZE
descriptionHtml: Are you having trouble making long-term changes and keeping the motivation to be physically active? Do you want to be strong, healthy, happy, and functionally fit as you age? The Lift With Khy app allows you to log in to track your health and fitness progress. Whether you meet with me, make it to the gym on your own, or have some time at home to spare, I’ll be with you every step of the way. It’s as simple as opening the app, logging in, and viewing what your workouts are for the week. This app allows you to take progress pictures, view How-To videos of the exercises, and link your MYFITNESSPAL menu, among other things. Remember, together we can make it happen.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
“We’ve introduced the ability to edit and delete in-app messages. Just one more way we’re making client-trainer communication a whole lot easier.
As usual, we’ve also made some other back-end upgrades to make your experience even better.”

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
As much as we’d all like, big changes unfortunately don’t happen overnight. That’s why we’ve introduced habit coaching—a new way to help clients make small, sustainable lifestyle changes! Trainers can now create habits within our Master Habit Library and prescribe them to clients. As clients complete habits each day, they will earn habit streaks and unlock special achievement badges over time.
As always, we’ve also made some back-end upgrades and bug fixes to make your experience even better.
